### A voice with Fibonacci-weighted harmonics

**Fibonacci sequence** (1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13…) as harmonic weights.

```scheme
;; Fibonacci weights: 1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13 (normalized)
(define fib-profile
  (let ((fibs '(0 1 1 2 3 5 8 13)))
    (map (lambda (f) (/ f 13.0)) fibs)))

;; *[needs: GAP-6]*
;; (define-voice 'fibonacci (fib-profile '(0 0 0 0 0 0 0 0)))

(define (fib-chord)
  (note 48 'whole 80)
  (note 55 'whole 80)
  (note 60 'whole 80))

(fib-chord)
```

<!-- BUILD: a naturally growing spectral shape -->

[VISUAL: Spectrum with bars growing according to the Fibonacci sequence. Label: \"Fibonacci-weighted harmonics.\"]

