(define (two-formant-scale)
  (note 60 'quarter 75)
  (note 62 'quarter 75)
  (note 64 'quarter 75)
  (note 65 'quarter 75))

(two-formant-scale)
```

<!-- BUILD: a more vowel-like, vocal quality -->

[VISUAL: Spectrum with two peaks — at the 3rd and 7th harmonics. Label: \"Two formants — vowel-like spectrum.\"]

